omewhere. Follow him. What is he looking at? Is that another bear? No... to small. It is your mom! But that means you have to leave your friend behind. Once you get back to your mom, keep on meowing, you can still hear him, but now you can't. The en- wait! You wake up in the middle of the night, go to the star, and you can see him. You can even meow, he roars back happily.Edit: I did leave out a alot of things, and also I found out that you can escape the fox.Edit 2: Also, sorry if I made a few spelling mistakes, I just type fast, I guess. Also I wanted to move on to something after this review."
